sentences: Dwayne Megens (born September 6, 1994 in Eindhoven, Netherlands), better known by his stage name D-wayne, is a Dutch house music DJ and record producer.
He releases materials through Nervous specialized house label, Steve Aoki's Dim Mak label, Spinnin' Records and most recently on Wall Recordings, Afrojack's record label.
He released his single "Quantum" in 2013 and collaborated with Dutch DJ Afrojack in "Freedom" featuring Jack McManus.
